            rulePageRuleText49: "4.6. All personal data collected and processed by the site is stored on a server that is not accessible outside the protected corporate network.",  
            rulePageRuleText50: "4.7. The User of the site can request the deletion of their personal data. In such a case, all collected personal information will be deleted, and future access to the site using that information will not be guaranteed.",  
