            rulePageRuleText52: "4.9. The user is responsible for the accuracy and correctness of any information and data they provide.",  
            rulePageRuleText53: "5. Cookies, web beacons, and similar technologies",  
            rulePageRuleText54: "5.1 The site may use cookies, web beacons, and other similar technologies to store information, as well as to improve the quality of services provided (including security), as well as for advertising purposes.",  
            rulePageRuleText55: "5.2. Cookies are data stored in a user's browser and sent back to the site upon subsequent visits. Cookies facilitate the use of the site and collect statistics. Cookies do not contain personal data.",  
